1
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,600
But if you're impatient,

2
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,520
<i>you could just write a will yourself.</i>

3
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,240
<i>Type it out and forge the signature.</i>

4
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:31,480
And do you really think he'd be happy
having a murderer for a mother?

5
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,360
You know too much now!

6
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,720
Yai is here.

7
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,680
<i>Gather everyone now.</i>

8
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,960
Yai!

9
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,520
On was pregnant?

10
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,960
<i>On had a miscarriage because of you.</i>

11
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,640
You killed your own child, you bastard.

12
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:18,520
Pin. Wait for me.

13
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,760
This time, it has to end.

14
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,240
Please don't come here, Mr. Yai.

15
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,280
You mustn't.

16
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:59,440
Tell them not to let the drinking
mess up the job tomorrow.

17
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,920
Yai will definitely come.

18
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:05,600
If we catch him this time,
I'll reward everyone.

19
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:09,560
Thank you, Madam. Don't worry about it.

20
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:12,240
We're fully prepared to welcome them.

21
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,720
Let them come.

22
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,800
Not even an ant could escape.

23
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:20,160
You should also increase
the security at the resort.

24
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:24,280
Just in case Yai gets any stupid ideas
and tries to rescue Pin.

25
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:27,040
If that's happens,
we'll get rid of him tonight.

26
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,080
Yes.

27
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,680
Yai, I've set a meeting with my professor.

28
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,320
We'll go to the police station at nine.

29
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,600
Yai. Hey, Yai.

30
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,720
Yai, where are you? Hey.

31
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,560
And there it is.

32
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,240
CHIEF YAM

33
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,560
Yai, you left it here
so I couldn't contact you?

34
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,800
You sly dog.

35
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,440
Chief, how are things there?

36
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,840
<i>Mr. Tong has woken up, Mr. Yai.</i>

37
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,280
This is Pan speaking. I'll be right there.

38
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,680
Uncle Win, Yai ran away.

39
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,440
Piak's gone too.

40
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,320
I need to hurry and check on Mr. Tong.

41
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,600
Stay here in case Yai reaches out.

42
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,960
- Hey, stop right there.
- Hey.

43
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,280
I'm here to deliver the ice.

44
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:36,680
Take off your hat.

45
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,800
Don't worry, I already did the swab.

46
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:45,280
Only one line showed up.

47
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:48,120
But I don't know
why I'm feeling like I have a cold.

48
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,000
My nose is a bit stuffy.

49
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,040
But there was only one line, really.

50
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,920
Okay, okay. Go.

51
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,040
Yes.

52
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,640
Na.

53
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,400
Why aren't you dressed yet?

54
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,920
It's almost time.

55
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:15,200
Na, did you hear what I said?

56
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,080
Are you okay?

57
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,040
Can we…

58
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,280
postpone the wedding?

59
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,200
What are you saying?

60
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:29,600
Why are you being dramatic now?

61
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,560
Have you forgotten
that we need to lure Yai out?

62
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:36,200
And if we can't catch him this time,
we're all dead.

63
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,520
We don't have time.

64
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,640
Get up and get dressed now.

65
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,160
Hurry up.

66
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,800
I'm delivering ice.

67
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,040
The ice factory just delivered it.

68
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,600
Their sack is over there.

69
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,320
But Madam called to order it herself.

70
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:01,200
Well, then just pour it
into the ice chest.

71
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,000
I need to go to the bathroom.

72
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,720
I'm about to pee myself.

73
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,520
I can't hold it in anymore.

74
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:25,920
You look so good.

75
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,720
Here comes the bride.

76
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:54,640
So beautiful and lovely,
my dear daughter-in-law.

77
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,160
Are you making Pin marry Mr. Na?

78
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,680
You can't do that, Madam.

79
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,680
You know I love Pin.

80
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:22,000
You're such a hot-headed young man.

81
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,880
Calm down and listen to me first.

82
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:28,680
It's just a trick to lure Yai out.

83
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:33,000
If we spread the news
that Pin is marrying Na,

84
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,720
he won't be able to keep his cool.

85
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:40,120
Calm down. Trust me. Just calm down.

86
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:03,240
Care for some orange juice, Boss?

87
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,160
Orange juice?

88
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,320
Orange juice.

89
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,880
Alright. Since Pin

90
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,400
has no relatives left,

91
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:20,360
we should shorten
the ceremony to save time.

92
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:23,120
Put on the ring, do the water blessing,

93
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:26,240
enter the bridal suite,
and then it's over.

94
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,560
Na.

95
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:31,800
Put the ring on Pin. Give him the ring.

96
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:18,240
I locked Noi in the workers' cabin.

97
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,160
Do you want to see her die?

98
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,120
Don't come near me.

99
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,840
Go ahead and stab yourself.

100
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,360
I don't care if you die.

101
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:13,880
No. If Pin dies, I'll die too.

102
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:23,960
Pin, put the glass down
and let's talk it out.

103
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:28,720
No, I won't talk to a monster like you.

104
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:33,200
You're a woman, yet you force
other women to commit immoral acts.

105
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:36,120
You destroy their human dignity.

106
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:39,280
You can't even tell the difference
between good and evil.

107
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,480
Well said.

108
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:58,120
Such a strong spirit is worthy
of being the wife of Bandit Yai.

109
00:12:58,760 --> 00:12:59,600
Mr. Yai?

110
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:06,880
I'd rather die than marry someone else.

111
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,600
Did you hear what my wife said, Na?

112
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,640
You've always taken everything from me.

113
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:20,200
But Pin? Don't even think about it.

114
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:28,480
Hi, Mr. Yai. Good to see you again.

115
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:32,680
I didn't expect you to come alone.

116
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:35,320
Where's the Bandit Yai Gang?

117
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:39,120
I'm more than capable
of handling you on my own.

118
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,960
Last time you were lucky,

119
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:44,360
but this time,
I won't make the same mistake.

120
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,240
Hey.

121
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,360
Pin, stand behind me.

122
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:07,280
Now.

123
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,680
Dying for a woman?

124
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:15,880
Men are truly foolish creatures.

125
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:18,160
You're too twisted to ever understand.

126
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,160
That's why you and I cannot coexist.

127
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,040
Kill him!

128
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,920
Don't shoot.

129
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,920
Shoot him!

130
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,440
It's about time.

131
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:29,000
Sommai? Sommai!

132
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:36,120
What's going on? Get up.

133
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:38,720
What a shame.

134
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:41,000
I went to the trouble
of buying an expensive toy gun.

135
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,960
Why? Why are they like this, Mr. Yai?

136
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:49,560
They're…

137
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:11,360
This method is simple.

138
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:14,880
Just sprinkle some pepper… No.

139
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:18,480
Just sprinkle some arsenic, and cardiac
arrest will follow almost instantly.

140
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,640
No need to waste effort or bullets.

141
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,840
I just used your method.

142
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,520
You…

143
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,360
- Pin.
- Auntie, no!

144
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:32,880
Enough, Auntie. Stop it.

145
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,320
Auntie!

146
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:40,640
Auntie. Auntie!

147
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,040
Auntie.

148
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:48,520
Auntie! Aunt…

149
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,800
Mr. Na?

150
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:05,680
They're not dead, are they?

151
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:07,960
You promised you wouldn't break the law.

152
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:09,680
It's just a heavy sedative.

153
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:11,440
They'll wake up tomorrow morning.

154
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:12,480
Let's go, Pin.

155
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:19,960
Open the door! I said open the door!

156
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,920
Come on, open it, Auntie!

157
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,680
Run, Pin.

158
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,920
That bike. Hurry.

159
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,440
Noi. Noi's being held
at the workers' cabin.

160
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,720
Don't worry, Piak's helping her.

161
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:41,440
But I left the evidence
against Madam at the resort.

162
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:43,440
- I need to go get it.
- Pin.

163
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:46,640
It's too late. Focus on surviving
and hop on, fast!

164
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,400
Hey!

165
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:57,360
Damn it!

166
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,640
Go get them!

167
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,720
They can't catch up to us now, Mr. Yai.

168
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:25,680
We're safe once we get out of here.

169
00:18:26,840 --> 00:18:30,120
When they were
about to shoot you, I was terrified.

170
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:33,400
That Tsunami wouldn't let you get shot.

171
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:36,280
I was terrified for you.

172
00:18:36,360 --> 00:18:38,560
I was starting to think
you were actually insane.

173
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:42,080
Going up against them with a gun like that
would only lead to your death.

174
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,640
So, was I cool?

175
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:47,680
Not at all. But you looked so great.

176
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:51,800
This is what they call
being madly in love with your husband.

177
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:07,080
- Mr. Yai?
- Careful.

178
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:09,880
Mr. Yai. Mr. Yai!

179
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,840
Mr. Yai. Mr. Yai.

180
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:16,600
Pin, be careful. Run away first. Run away.

181
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,560
No, I won't run away.

182
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:20,160
Mr. Yai…

183
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:30,320
You coward. Quit the cheap shots.

184
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,600
Come out and face me.

185
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:40,640
Jom?

186
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:45,760
Yai. I've been waiting
for you for a long time.

187
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,880
You must have seen
the henchman passed out at the back.

188
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,480
Don't, Jom.

189
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,480
Mr. Tong.

190
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,800
Do you remember how you ended up in a pit?

191
00:20:18,080 --> 00:20:19,960
Mr. Yai saved your life.

192
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,880
Do you remember who tried to kill you?

193
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:35,840
Why is this happening?

194
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:37,560
Please wait outside for a moment.

195
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:48,760
Jom! Jom, stop! Jom!

196
00:20:49,840 --> 00:20:51,800
Jom, stop right now!

197
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:53,600
Stop it!

198
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:56,920
Mr. Yai…

199
00:20:57,880 --> 00:21:00,280
I've changed my mind. I won't kill you.

200
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:03,720
But you must write a letter

201
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:06,640
confessing that you murdered Un and Pha.

202
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,640
Then, I'll let you go.

203
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:13,200
And do I need to mention

204
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,640
that you were having an affair with Pha?

205
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:20,920
That you came to Dad with two kids
yet claimed to be a virgin?

206
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,480
Shut up!

207
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:25,120
You're such a foul-mouthed bastard.

208
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,280
That's why Paisal hated you!

209
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:27,520
It all started with you.

210
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:29,440
You're a heartless woman

211
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:32,240
who poisoned my father
and others for your own profit.

212
00:21:32,320 --> 00:21:33,800
Your father deserved to die!

213
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:36,480
He lied to me.

214
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,120
He never told me that he had a son.

215
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:44,640
He sold me a dream that
I would take over the Paisal Farm empire.

216
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,960
And look what happened.

217
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:47,440
I ended up dealing with a brat like you!

218
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:51,920
Your father is just like every other man

219
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:54,480
who wants me to satisfy his lust.

220
00:21:54,560 --> 00:21:56,360
But I'm not stupid.

221
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,800
I'm not a whore.

222
00:21:58,480 --> 00:22:01,160
I'm just trying to survive
and protect myself and my children.

223
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,720
And what did I do wrong?

224
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:05,080
I was only 14 back then.

225
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:08,840
I lost my mother,
so I needed love from my father,

226
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:10,840
just like your children need it from you.

227
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:14,960
You protect your own children,

228
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:17,080
but you hurt other people's children.

229
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:20,600
You accused me, forcing me to flee,
without caring if I lived or died.

230
00:22:22,120 --> 00:22:24,840
You'll never understand
how to be a mother.

231
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,800
You're just a woman with a uterus,
but you can't really be a mother!

232
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:30,080
- You bastard!
- Madam!

233
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,960
- You asshole! I'll kill you!
- Madam!

234
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:34,840
Madam! Just kill me instead.
I'm ready to die!

235
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,520
- Sommai.
- Yes?

236
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:38,360
Take Pin and lock her up separately.

237
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:42,240
- Come here!
- Let go of me.

238
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:45,000
Don't worry about me. Save yourself.

239
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:46,720
You have to stay for me, Pin.

240
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:48,480
Come here!

241
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:50,880
Mr. Yai. Mr. Yai.

242
00:22:52,360 --> 00:22:53,200
Jom.

243
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:58,600
If you want Pinanong to be your wife…

244
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:03,120
you have to kill him with your own hands.

245
00:23:05,040 --> 00:23:06,640
I'll give him to you.

246
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:09,560
But if he doesn't die,

247
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:13,000
Pin will never be yours.

248
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:42,040
Get in here!

249
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,040
Stay still!

250
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,280
Go!

251
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,640
It's not too late to change, Jom.

252
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:32,840
Uncle Win is very worried about you.

253
00:24:33,560 --> 00:24:35,880
Don't you think you should
go back to him and be a good son?

254
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:38,200
And you think you were such a good son?

255
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,920
You yourself were an ungrateful brat too.

256
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,800
And do you want to end up like me, Jom?

257
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,440
It's because of you

258
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,840
that Dad cut me off.

259
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:50,120
I hate you, Yai.

260
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:52,600
You took my father from me.

261
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,720
You took Pin from me.

262
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:58,920
But today

263
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,240
I've beaten you.

264
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:10,920
Killing me while I'm tied up

265
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:13,400
doesn't count as a win.

266
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,640
You're just a coward.

267
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:20,800
If you're truly a competent man,

268
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:23,080
face me one-on-one.

269
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:27,560
If I lose, you can kill me.

270
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:35,360
But I don't think a loser like you

271
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,480
would dare.

272
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:02,200
<i>My daughter is still alive.</i>

273
00:26:02,280 --> 00:26:03,600
<i>But my grandchild…</i>

274
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:07,880
<i>the one in On's womb</i>
<i>never got the chance to see the world</i>

275
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:10,240
<i>because of its father's selfishness.</i>

276
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:26,760
Why do you have
to think about it over and over?

277
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:35,080
It's not your fault.

278
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,480
It's not your fault!

279
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:41,320
<i>On had a miscarriage because of you.</i>

280
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:45,360
<i>You killed your own child, you bastard.</i>

281
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:52,640
My head's about to explode!

282
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:56,080
Stop thinking. Stop thinking!

283
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:51,920
I'm a terrible person, On.

284
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,920
I'm a terrible person.

285
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:17,560
Na! Help me, Na! Na!

286
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,880
Na!

287
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:25,640
Na, can you hear me? Help me!

288
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,560
Na!

289
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:46,840
‪Hey.

290
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,120
- Pin.
- Mr. Yai?

291
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,120
You're bleeding again.

292
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,720
- Sit down first. I'll stop the bleeding.
- No need, Pin. I can handle it.

293
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:35,160
We need to get out of here.

294
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,120
Jom.

295
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:48,360
You need to stop hurting people.

296
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:50,320
It's him who's hurting others.

297
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:54,280
Pin, you love him so much

298
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:57,560
that you're willing to cooperate
with him to trick me?

299
00:30:58,480 --> 00:31:00,240
How could you do this to me?

300
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:04,160
I just wanted to find out
who killed my mother.

301
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:05,840
I have no ill intentions toward you.

302
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,840
No ill intentions?

303
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:12,880
But what you did is killing me slowly.

304
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:16,360
I was stupid to fall in love with you.

305
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:19,040
You don't love Pin.
You only love yourself.

306
00:31:19,120 --> 00:31:22,440
You just want Pin, and when you can't
have her, you're lashing out at me.

307
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:25,760
No! It's because you're evil!

308
00:31:26,280 --> 00:31:27,440
You killed Aunt Un.

309
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:31,280
- You deserve to die!
- It's not that easy.

310
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:36,520
Mr. Yai.

311
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:41,880
Jom, Mr. Yai didn't kill my mom.

312
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:44,160
Are you still taking his side?

313
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:47,960
If you want to know
who the real killer is,

314
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,760
just listen to this yourself.

315
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:21,400
The bug

316
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:25,240
can be connected
with my phone via the app?

317
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:32,840
<i>I activated the bug</i>
<i>by calling it with my phone beforehand.</i>

318
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,520
<i>As soon as someone spoke,</i>

319
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:36,800
<i>the device would turn on automatically</i>

320
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:40,200
<i>and immediately call my phone,</i>
<i>which was on silent mode.</i>

321
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:51,200
<i>The reason I came back</i>

322
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:54,360
<i>was because I wanted to know</i>
<i>how you could be cruel enough</i>

323
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:58,600
<i>to kill even the person</i>
<i>who loved you with all her heart.</i>

324
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:01,680
<i>Because there was someone</i>
<i>I loved more than Un.</i>

325
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:03,960
<i>I had no choice but to choose.</i>

326
00:33:10,160 --> 00:33:11,720
Madam killed Aunt Un?

327
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:17,840
She tricked me into going there
to frame me as a murderer.

328
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:21,920
Do you understand now?

329
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,840
Mr. Yai came to help Pin.

330
00:33:43,760 --> 00:33:47,480
So that means Pin is safe now, right?

331
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:57,120
Pin and Mr. Yai are locked up.

332
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:00,320
I don't know how they're doing right now.

333
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:06,160
Na, we need to go help them.

334
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,600
Let's go.

335
00:34:17,679 --> 00:34:20,840
Na, why did you take the gun out?

336
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:23,239
That's my gun, isn't it?

337
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,560
I want to die, Auntie.

338
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:35,120
Are you crazy?

339
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:39,719
What are you talking about?

340
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:42,920
I've done everything for you.

341
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:47,199
Hey, come with me.

342
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:49,199
I'll take you to meet Pin in your suite.

343
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,440
Come, come with me.

344
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:52,400
I killed my own child.

345
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:56,880
I caused my child's death, Auntie.

346
00:35:00,520 --> 00:35:02,720
What are you talking about?

347
00:35:03,400 --> 00:35:05,400
Before On was taken to demand the ransom…

348
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:10,400
she was pregnant.

349
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:14,920
I didn't go help her.

350
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:18,320
And On miscarried.

351
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:21,640
I killed my own child.

352
00:35:22,160 --> 00:35:24,080
I killed my own child!

353
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:33,400
This is the karma you've created.

354
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,800
Please stop committing sins.

355
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:39,320
Are you crazy? It was just an embryo.

356
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:46,480
Na, you don't have to feel sorry.

357
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:50,720
Once you're settled with Pin,
you can have as many children as you want.

358
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:53,560
Don't be sorry, okay?

359
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:58,320
Madam.

360
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:01,840
That bastard Tong is still alive.

361
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,800
He told the police that you killed him

362
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:05,360
and also accused you of killing Un.

363
00:36:06,160 --> 00:36:07,960
The police are raiding the farm.

364
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:09,560
We need to run.

365
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:11,520
What did you say?

366
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,680
Sommai!

367
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:47,760
This way.

368
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,200
You two wait here.

369
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,360
I'll go get us our ride.

370
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:03,440
If we go together, someone will see us.

371
00:37:03,520 --> 00:37:05,000
Be careful, Jom.

372
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,480
- Run.
- Mr. Yai.

373
00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:19,800
Get Pin out of here. I'll hold them back.

374
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:21,400
No, Jom.

375
00:37:24,120 --> 00:37:26,120
I'm wearing
a bulletproof vest, don't worry.

376
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:28,400
Mr. Yai, please get her out of here.

377
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,240
Wait, Jom.

378
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:31,240
Damn it.

379
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,040
Come on.

380
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:52,480
Let's go.

381
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:29,040
Get up. Get up.

382
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,880
This is the last thing

383
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,440
I can do for you, Pin.

384
00:39:14,640 --> 00:39:16,240
This way, Officer.

385
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,080
- Sergeant.
- Sir.

386
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:26,840
- Search the upper floor.
- Yes, sir!

387
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,640
Freeze! Police!

388
00:39:31,200 --> 00:39:33,040
Freeze! Search everywhere, Sergeant.

389
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:33,960
- Yes, sir.
- Roger.

390
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:43,760
The doctor injected a heart stimulant
so Tong could talk, Dad.

391
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,440
But Madam got away.

392
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:48,240
I don't think she'll get far, Pan.

393
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:54,880
Dispatch, pursue the criminal immediately.

394
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:56,240
The criminal has escaped. Over.

395
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,240
Come on, Pin.

396
00:40:12,520 --> 00:40:13,360
Mr. Yai.

397
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,960
Mr. Pan is taking the police
to question Tong at the hospital.

398
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:21,040
Tong pointed the finger at Madam Krongsuk

399
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,640
for Aunt Unreuan's murder.

400
00:40:22,720 --> 00:40:25,400
The police are sending a unit
to arrest her.

401
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:27,320
So, Uncle Pload has been released, right?

402
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:28,400
That's right.

403
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:31,320
Mr. Yai, where is Jom?

404
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:34,280
Jom helped us escape.

405
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:35,720
I don't know how he's doing now.

406
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:39,040
Phong, take care of Pin for me.

407
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:40,560
I'll go help Jom with Uncle Win.

408
00:40:40,640 --> 00:40:41,680
Yes.

409
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:48,560
Ms. Pin? Ms. Pin.

410
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:50,600
Ms. Pin was shot, Mr. Yai!

411
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:51,520
Pin?

412
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:53,440
Pin.

413
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:57,680
Pin.

414
00:40:58,240 --> 00:40:59,080
Let's go.

415
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:06,360
Don't worry about me. Go help Jom.

416
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:08,600
Go help Jom.

417
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:11,640
It's okay. Take Pin to a doctor.

418
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:12,920
I'll go check on Jom myself.

419
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,840
Phong, go with Uncle Win.

420
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,400
Protect him for me.

421
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:18,840
Yes, Mr. Yai.

422
00:41:20,120 --> 00:41:20,960
‪Pin.

423
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:22,480
Hang in there.

424
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:24,000
I'll get you to the hospital, Pin.

425
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:26,000
Mr. Yai…

426
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,560
Mr. Yai…

427
00:41:31,760 --> 00:41:34,240
I want to see your face one last time

428
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:39,280
before I lose the chance
to ever see you again.

429
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:46,200
No, Pin, you'll be okay.

430
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,720
We have to stay together.

431
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:51,680
Pin. Pin!

432
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:54,720
Pin! Pin!

433
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:57,640
Pin! Pin!

434
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:00,360
You witch.

435
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:03,160
Where are you? I'm going to kill you!

436
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:25,960
Who are you? Where are you taking me?

437
00:42:41,120 --> 00:42:43,880
Jom! Jom!

438
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:45,360
Jom!

439
00:42:46,720 --> 00:42:48,800
Ms. Jin? What are you doing here?

440
00:42:49,880 --> 00:42:52,200
Pan asked me to help find Pin and Mr. Yai,

441
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,440
but Jom called.

442
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:56,400
His voice sounded terrible.

443
00:42:59,600 --> 00:43:01,040
Please be okay, Jom.

444
00:43:02,120 --> 00:43:03,960
Jom, where are you? Jom!

445
00:43:04,680 --> 00:43:05,840
I'm here!

446
00:43:07,080 --> 00:43:09,680
Jom, you're my son.

447
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,600
I love you.

448
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,080
Jom.

449
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:17,680
Dad…

450
00:43:23,160 --> 00:43:26,080
Jom! Uncle Win! Jom!

451
00:43:31,800 --> 00:43:33,440
- Jom.
- Jom!

452
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:38,160
Jom. Jom, my son!

453
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:52,160
Hey, can you tell me now

454
00:43:52,240 --> 00:43:53,840
why you brought us here?

455
00:43:54,680 --> 00:43:55,880
Or is it about the money?

456
00:43:57,880 --> 00:44:01,880
Let me and my children go,
and I'll get you the money.

457
00:44:06,920 --> 00:44:07,800
Children?

458
00:44:08,640 --> 00:44:12,840
Or… Oh, were you a worker at Paisal Farm

459
00:44:12,920 --> 00:44:14,720
who got angry for getting fired?

460
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:17,760
How could I be angry at my dear lover?

461
00:44:22,560 --> 00:44:25,720
Out of these two, only one will survive.
Choose. Now!

462
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,280
Freeze! Police!

463
00:44:31,360 --> 00:44:32,600
Shoot to open a path!

464
00:44:32,680 --> 00:44:34,720
I don't want anything from him!

465
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:39,920
<i>We're going to have a child together.</i>

466
00:44:40,000 --> 00:44:41,120
The doctor said

467
00:44:42,320 --> 00:44:43,520
you're pregnant.

468
00:45:27,440 --> 00:45:30,280
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul
